Spotify new mobile UI roll out
text:
Anyone know if Spotify measures UI usage? I find the new UI unusable for browsing.

I'd like to think they're distinguishing between the various forms of usage like search, home screen, library (I know I would). I'm tempted to forego the app entirely. But my wife didn't get the update and my playlists are still usable.

PS, If anyone here worked on the new UI; how about giving us guinea pigs an opt out option?
